name: Shut the front door Foyer Sign
description: Made famous by the East Coast Creative girls!  Comes unpainted on 1/8 inch eucalyptus; use velcro command strips to hang.   Letters are 8-10 inches high.

name: Chalkboard Painted Pennant Banner
description:
Have a Pennant Banner you can use for every occasion; you can customize it yourself!  

Each pennant is 4 inches long; this listing is for 15 pennants. Made on heat pressed eucalyptus; no glue or formaldehyde!

Want the unpainted version?  Something larger?  We can do that too; just let us know what you'd prefer!

name: Reclaimed Hardwood Flooring Signs
description:
Featured on Fieldstone Hill Designs and Holly Mathis Interiors!  Snap up one of these custom stamped signs while we still have flooring in stock.

  The wood was purchased from an old Maine Farmhouse that was set for demolition in the central part of the state about a decade ago.

Bring some artful history into your home!

 The signs can be any size up to 11 x 13 so they can ship in a flat-rate box; either let us know the message you want during Paypal, or contact us at 163designcompany@gmail.com to set up a custom order!

name: Custom Silhouette
description:
Send us your jpg or pdf profile picture and we'll laser a custom silhouette!  We popped ours into a frame with sticky tack; I wrote the date on the back, and I plan on doing a new one every year and amassing a fun collection. :)  They come unpainted on 1/8th inch heat pressed eucalyptus and are approx. 6 1/2 inches wide. {The pictured silhouettes are painted in chalkboard paint}.

Our email address is 163designcompany@gmail.com for questions!
